# Design Guidelines for elf.baby Project

## Visual Design Rules

### Shadows
- **DO NOT** add shadows to any elements when creating new functionality
- Avoid using `shadow-*` Tailwind classes or CSS `box-shadow` properties

### Border Radius

#### General Elements
- **Maximum border radius**: 5px
- Use `rounded-[5px]` or `rounded-sm` (4px) in Tailwind
- Never exceed 5px for any element

#### Buttons
- **Border radius**: 3px
- Use `rounded-[3px]` in Tailwind
- Apply consistently to all button elements

#### Images
- **Border radius**: 3px
- Use `rounded-[3px]` in Tailwind
- Apply to all image elements (`<img>`, `<Image>`, etc.)

## Implementation Notes

When writing code:
- Always follow these border radius rules
- Never add shadow effects to new components
- Use Tailwind classes: `rounded-[3px]` for buttons/images, `rounded-[5px]` max for other elements
- If using inline styles, ensure they comply with these limits

